            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gematsu.com/2025/04/elden-ring-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-30-million<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Five million units sold since June 2024.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Total worldwide shipments and digital sales for <em><a title="Games > Elden Ring [31 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/elden-ring">Elden Ring</a></em> have surpassed 30 million units, publisher <a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,676 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco</a> and developer <a title="Companies > FromSoftware [394 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/kadokawa-corporation/fromsoftware">FromSoftware</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/fromsoftware_pr/status/1916855043644625374" rel="noopener" target="_blank">announced</a>. <span id="more-961780"></span></p><p>The <a title="Genres > Open-World [621 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/open-world">open-world</a> <a title="Genres > Action RPG [1,597 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg/action-rpg">action RPG</a> was <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/06/elden-ring-shipments-and-digital-sales-top-25-million">last reported</a> to have shipped 25 million units as of June 2024, meaning an additional five million units have been moved since.</p><p><em>Elden Ring</em> launched for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,356 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,114 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [27,945 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [13,933 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,021 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1245620/ELDEN_RING/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on February 25, 2022 worldwide, followed by the major expansion “Shadow of the Erdtree” on June 21, 2024. A Switch 2 version is <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/04/elden-ring-tarnished-edition-announced-for-switch-2">due out in 2025</a>.</p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
